<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l1">Wir ~ die <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> deʒ Rats
                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>Bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>offenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l2">mit <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe / daʒ vvir frıcʒen
            Kleınen gancʒen vnd vollen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l3">gewalt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / vor des aller / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l4"><expan>durhlewhtigıſt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> /
              <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Ruprehts <expan>Römiſche<ex>n</ex></expan> Künigs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l5">cʒü allen <expan>cʒeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mer<ex>er</ex>s</expan> des Reıchs <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> hofgerıchte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l6">fürpot cʒu nemen / auf Güten Jüdin vveilunt des Jacob Rappen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l7">Juden <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> vvitben / Mıchel / Laʒaren / vnd Moſſe dıe Juden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l8"><expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Rappen Süne / vnd Hendlein
            Jüdin ſein <expan>tocht<ex>er</ex></expan> / . vnd ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l9">vmb ſölıch klage vordrung vnd cʒüſprüche als vvir cʒü Jn
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l10">vor <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> hofgericht cʒü beklagen vnd das
                <expan>cʒevord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l11">ſtat cʒü gewinne vnd cʒü verluſt vnd cʒü
              <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Mit <expan>Vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r2l12"><expan>at<ex>er</ex>go</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>ıs</expan>
<expan>Bap<ex>tiſ</ex>te</expan> Anno ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_228" id="112v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
