<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> dez rats
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czü
                                                  <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>offenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit
                                                  <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe, daz wir
                                                Friczen Kleinen ganczen und vollen gewalt
                                                  <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> vor des aller
                                                  <expan>durhlewhtigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Ruprehts,
                                                  <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> künigs, czü
                                                allen <expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mer<ex>er</ex>s</expan> des reichs,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, hofgerichte fürpot
                                                czu nemen auf Güten, jüdin, weilunt des Jacob
                                                Rappen, juden <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, witben, Michel
                                                Lazaren und Mosse, die juden,
                                                  <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Rappen süne, und
                                                Hendlein, jüdin, sein
                                                  <expan>tocht<ex>er</ex></expan>; und sie umb
                                                sölich klage vordrung und czüsprüche, als wir czü in
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, vor
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> hofgericht czü
                                                beklagen und das <expan>czevord<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                                                an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat czü gewinne
                                                und czü verlust und czü
                                                  <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; mit
                                                  <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
<expan>at<ex>er</ex>go</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>is</expan>
<expan>bap<ex>tis</ex>te</expan> anno ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
